                <button onclick="askCopilot('Show compliance status summary')" class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-white dark:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-50 dark:hover:bg-emerald-900 transition-colors">
                    ‚úÖ Compliance
