                <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-700 p-3 rounded-lg rounded-tl-none max-w-[280px]">
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
                        Hello! I'm Shahin AI, your GRC intelligence assistant. I can help you with:
